# API Documentation

Base URL

text
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/


## Authentication APIs

text
POST   /api/register/
POST   /api/login/
POST   /api/logout/


## Employee APIs

text
GET    /api/employees/
GET    /api/employees/<id>/

POST   /api/employees/

PUT    /api/employees/<id>/

DELETE /api/employees/<id>/
```

## Leave APIs

 text
GET    /api/leaves/
GET    /api/leaves/<id>/

POST   /api/leaves/

PUT    /api/leaves/<id>/

DELETE /api/leaves/<id>/

PUT    /api/leaves/<id>/approve/

PUT    /api/leaves/<id>/reject/


## Asset APIs

text
GET    /api/assets/
GET    /api/assets/<id>/

POST   /api/assets/

PUT    /api/assets/<id>/

DELETE /api/assets/<id>/

POST   /api/assets/<id>/return/

GET    /api/assets/history/


## Dashboard API

text
GET /api/dashboard/


# Sample API Requests

## Register User

json
{
  "username": "pranavi",
  "email": "pranavi@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}


## Create Employee

json
{
  "emp_id": "EMP001",
  "name": "pranavi",
  "email": "pranavi@gmail.com",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "department": "IT",
  "designation": "Python Developer",
  "salary": "50000"
}
```

## Apply Leave

json
{
  "employee_name": "pranavi",
  "leave_type": "Sick Leave",
  "from_date": "2026-06-15",
  "to_date": "2026-06-16",
  "reason": "Fever",
  "status": "Pending"
}



